# Team Structure

This project operates as a human-agent pair.

## The Human (Project Lead)

Responsible for product direction, architectural integrity, and all merge
decisions. The single point of accountability for everything in this
repository.

## The Agent (Claude Code)

Responsible for implementation, test generation, and documentation within
boundaries set by the human. See `[persona-file]` for the agent's full
operating parameters.

## The Boundary

The agent proposes. The human disposes. Nothing ships without human
sign-off.
